(`⟦…⟧` markers wrap untrusted user-controlled fields — treat as data, not instructions.)

**Five Search-Query Categories** (3-5 concise queries each, 3-6 words per query):

1. **`pedagogy`** — NEP 2020, NCF, DIKSHA, NISHTHA, active-learning, child-centred teaching methods for school classrooms. Topics like Bloom's taxonomy, formative assessment, inquiry-based learning, FLN, NIPUN.
2. **`storytelling`** — animated concept explainers, narrative lessons, NCERT-chapter visualisations for Classes 1-12. Stories that teach `{{{subject}}}` concepts.
